abstract: >-
  Conversational Q&A over a personal library of research papers, with
  citations that point back to the exact PDF page and section. Built on
  PydanticAI, LanceDB, and Anthropic Claude. Local-first, open source.
keywords:
  - retrieval-augmented generation
  - vector search
  - research papers
  - citation faithfulness
  - LanceDB
  - PydanticAI
license: MIT
